OL,5,G1605 Heatwave: Summer of '76
OL,6,     FThe extraordinary story of a
OL,7,     Fmassive national moment when
OL,8,     Fgardens burned, communities
OL,9,     Fdepended upon communal standpipes
OL,10,     Ffor their water and Brits were
OL,11,     Furged to "bath with a friend".
OL,12,G1735 The 1970s Kitchen: Everything We
OL,13,G     Loved & Lost
OL,14,     FIn this nostalgic show we chart
OL,15,     Fthe transformation of the British
OL,16,     Fkitchen, revealing the trends and
OL,17,     Fsocial changes that shaped the
OL,18,     Flook and of our kitchens in the
OL,19,     F70s.
