OL,12,G1800 The Directors
OL,13,     FStanley Kubrick is considered one
OL,14,     Fof the greatest and most
OL,15,     Finfluential directors in cinematic
OL,16,     Fhistory. His cinematic masterpiece
OL,17,     Fwas to arrive in 1968 with the
OL,18,     Fcreation of 2001: A Space Odyssey.
